• 0.5 = half (50%, 0.5x effect)

Used for gathering rates, craft speeds, etc.

Examples: 0.5, 1.0, 2.0, 5.0

Amount of currency or items required to upgrade a furnace.
Upgrades typically improve smelting speed or fuel efficiency.

Examples: 1000, 5000
